metadata.name: FREEDOM
metadata.description:
Freedom is like white clouds and a warm wind. Just look around, nature is very wise, pure, insanely beautiful, everything around us is made up of elements. If you try to hold fire, you are sure to get burned, if you want to take earth, water, wind in your fist, they will simply flow out or fall out of your palm. Everything around us is born free! Standing on the cliff at that moment the girl felt peace, tranquility, unity with nature, the warm summer wind was blowing her hair, and that was freedom - the highest value of man! 

There is meaning in life when there is freedom - the freedom to choose, the freedom to love, the freedom to do what you want and to fear nothing.
